  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Tunturi Hotel is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>All meals are served in the hotel's main reception building, approx. 100 metres from the hotel room buildings.</p>
<p>Each morning you can enjoy an extensive breakfast buffet which includes a continental offering with hot options.</p>
<p>A three course buffet dinner will be served each night, with a choice of main courses, including vegetarian option, two desserts, soup and a salad buffet.</p>
<p>New Years gala dinner and dance included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
