  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Tunturi Hotel is a wonderfully atmospheric hotel with a peaceful setting 250 metres from the village centre and next to the cross country ski tracks.  With cosy wood-panelled public areas, good cuisine and comfortable rooms, it provides good standard accommodation. Rooms are also available in the recently added luxury 4 star superior <a data-udi="umb://document/3d7dc001611746319bcefb1b23f134d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d7dc001611746319bcefb1b23f134d1}" title="Gielas Hotel">Gielas Hotel</a> building.</p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>The Hotel Tunturi has a peaceful location set back from the village, surrounded by lovely snowy forests and offers easy access to the cross country ski tracks. Ideally situated just a short distance from the main village, where you can find a handful of souvenir shops, cafes and restaurants, plus the toboggan slopes and bus stop taking you to the ski area.</p>
<h2>Cosy accommodation</h2>
<p>The main Tunturi building is where you'll find the reception and the restaurant, where you'll have your breakfast and evening meals.<span> It has a colourful history and its façade has features from functionalism, designed by a awarded Finnish architect Kurt Moberg.</span> The bedrooms and apartments are located in separate buildings nearby. This includes the superior four star <a data-udi="umb://document/3d7dc001611746319bcefb1b23f134d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d7dc001611746319bcefb1b23f134d1}" title="Gielas Hotel">Gielas Hotel</a> building, with its own cosy bar and restaurant for breakfast, is is one of our most popular <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a> hotels.  </p>
<h2>Lounge and bar </h2>
<p>After a day of exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka,</a> relax in the cosy and inviting public areas, decorated with wood panelling. <span>Enjoy a drink in the Bar &amp; Grill Pirtti which has a laid back home away from home feel, or sit back and relax with the live entertainment which if often on throughout the winter season. </span></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
